PLUGINS and finding them online
  Very similar to searching for a theme

FINDING PLUGINS

WordPress.org has only FREE plugins.

Google search for "___ plugin for wordpress"


PLUGIN INFORMATION

Two default plugins: Akismet (for site protection) and a Luis Armstrong quote machine

Types of Plugins: 
  Widget plugins, 
  Social plugins, 
  Backup/Security plugins, 
  Media plugins, 
  Custom Post Type and Field plugins,
  Form plugins,
  Membership plugins,
  SEO and Performance plugins,
  eCommerce plugins (to sell things on your site)
